<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٤١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7021">يَحْيَى بْنُ يَحْيَى: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">شَقِيقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6088">مَسْرُوقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِذَا أَنْفَقَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ مِنْ طَعَامِ بَيْتِهَا، غَيْرَ مُفْسِدَةٍ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَلَهَا أَجْرُهَا، وَلِلزَّوْجِ بِمَا اكْتَسَبَ، وَلِلْخَازِنِ مِثْلُ ذَلِكَ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>